gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 114, Raptors 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The 76ers defeated the Raptors, 114-107. Joel Embiid recorded 34 points (14-21 FG), nine rebounds and eight assists for the 76ers, while Tyrese Maxey added 34 points (12-20 FG, 7-9 3PM), six rebounds and seven assists in the victory. Scottie Barnes tallied 24 points, eight rebounds and five assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The 76ers improve to 1-1 on the season, while the Raptors fall to 1-2.
